metadata.name: Physical Coin  -  Bird Gang OG
metadata.description: The Bird Gang Coin is a black nickel 2.25" inch custom coin with laser engraved serial numbers for each coin.  From Gang Challenge games, to pulling the coolest low key flex, this coin is it.  This physical comes with a clear plastic capsule for protection, storage or display, an antique silver finish desktop coin stand for display and a custom designed flexible nylon coin holder which allows your coin to be held securely as a keychain, ornament, etc.  Trade in this NFT for your Physical Bird Gang Coin and accessories, collect two to upgrade your physical to a Trippy version, or 5 to create a custom 10 pack with your asset on the front.    ganGGang
